Command to log on to psql
-------------------------

psql -U postgres -d fitnesse_metrics_db

Command to create table
-----------------------

create table fitnesse_test (
     id integer default -1,
     test_name varchar(500),
     run_time_in_millis integer default -1,
     run_date timestamp default now(),
     status varchar(4) default '    ',
     host varchar(40) default '',
     ip_address varchar(16) default '',
     branch varchar(40) default '',
     sha varchar(40) default '',
     run integer default -1
);

Command to drop table
---------------------

drop table fitnesse_test;

